Package: openhantek
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: openhantek-firmware-hantek
Description: GUI application for Hantek USB oscilloscopes
 OpenHantek is a free software for Hantek (Voltcraft/Darkwire/Protek/Acetech)
 USB DSOs based on HantekDSO. The UI is written in C++/Qt5 and uses OpenGL to
 draw the graphs. It was tested with the DSO-2090; test results with other
 models are welcome.

Package: openhantek-firmware-hantek
Architecture: any
Depends: openhantek (>> ${source:Upstream-Version}),
         fxload,
         udev
Description: Firmware binary blobs for Hantek 2xxx series oscilloscopes
